所有程序包的分层结构

程序包分层结构:
  • demo,
  • demo.controller,
  • demo.domain,
  • demo.repository,
  • demo.security,
  • demo.service,
  • demo.session,
  • demo.validator

类分层结构

  • java.lang.Object
    • demo.session.HttpSessionConfig
    • demo.SpringSecuritySessionRedisUserDetailsServiceApplication
    • demo.SpringSecuritySessionRedisUserDetailsServiceApplicationTests
    • demo.domain.User
    • demo.controller.UserController
    • demo.domain.UserCreateForm
    • demo.validator.UserCreateFormValidator (implements org.springframework.validation.Validator)
    • demo.service.UserServiceImpl (implements demo.service.UserService)
    • org.springframework.security.config.annotation.web.configuration.WebSecurityConfigurerAdapter (implements org.springframework.security.config.annotation.web.WebSecurityConfigurer<T>)
      • demo.security.SecurityConfig

接口分层结构

  • org.springframework.data.repository.Repository<T,ID>
    • org.springframework.data.repository.CrudRepository<T,ID>
      • demo.repository.UserRepository
    • demo.repository.UserRepository
  • demo.service.UserService
